payanangal mudivathillai ( english : journeys never end ) is a 1982 indian tamil-language film directed by r. sundarrajan . the film stars mohan , poornima bhagyaraj in the lead roles . it was released on 26 february 1982 . the film was a blockbuster and completed a 300-day run at the box office . music was composed by ilaiyaraaja . both the lead actors won filmfare awards in their respective categories . it was remade in hindi as kalakar ( 1983 ) .